  title: "Survive. Extract. Profit."
  body: "Every raid costs fuel. Choose your location from the van\u2019s raid map
    and drop in. Enemies come in waves \u2014 each wave brings more fighters, and
    every few waves, a mini-boss joins the fray.\n\nYour only goal: get in, fight,
    and get out alive."
